$office$_night for CS:S
by Bryan and ZsebLowAg
============================================
Full Name : $office$_night
Map Type : AIM Combat/Skill
.BSP File : Size : 7184 Kb
.NAV File : Size : 113 Kb	
            Radar : Mark buy zone and all of the walls
Release Date : 2010.05.10.
Number Of Players : Maximum : 16v16
                    Recommended : 8v8
Custom Texture : NO
Custom Sound : NO
Custom Model : NO
===========================================
This is a $2000$ mod with office textures and office models. Modified walls ,4 ladders in the 4 corners, a big conference table, projector at the CT,T spawns, computer, plasma TV, book shelf, vending machine and 2 couch.  Four new weapons : 2 pieces of M3 SHOTGUN, 2 pieces of DEAGLE, 2 pieces of P228 COMPACT  and 1 piece of M249 MACHINE GUN. And WP changed to SCOUT. And a lot of little changes!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
===========================================
Installation :
Just extract the .BSP and .NAV file to your Counter Strike : Source directory 
( Steam/Steamapps/username/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps )
